page.html:
Regarding SOFT2
tbh im being boosted this far into the tournament. I'm really enjoying my matches and every match I've played. Seems like coming this far has made me a bit more known and it feels nice. I like this tournament a lot due to a mappool that I'm comfortable with. An all skillset mappool where I don't get dicked by acc gods! Focusing on being a well-rounded player is something I'm proud of and I guess has put in work in this tourny. And yeah, I don't really play mania anymore and this also affects the amount of practice I put into the mappool, but more recently I've been trying really hard to perform at a level I'm comfortable with. I know it is inevitable I will lose to someone better than me at some point, but in the end, this tournament has been a wonderful experience and is really the only thing that makes me play mania. Always enjoyed the game haha

pro player wannabe
what is this improvement
literally choke every ending of a good play
im literally all aim

quit mania until i get a new keyboard because keys ghost from too much game
also no longer motivated
still in SOFT2, having fun!
standard main now!

adore is still my favorite player
im seeking for an osu best friend to talk to all the time! ;w;
